    A TaxiRide is a taxi ride event. There are two types of events, a taxi ride start event and a taxi ride end event. The isStart flag specifies the type of the event. A TaxiRide consists of - the rideId of the event which is identical for start and end record - the time of the event - the longitude of the start location - the latitude of the start location - the longitude of the end location - the latitude of the end location - the passengerCnt of the ride - the travelDistance which is -1 for start events
